cs.CR, cs.DC, cs.SE, cs.AI, cs.NI

Reasoning: 
- cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) is the most likely category as the paper deals with detecting information leakage in cloud which is a security concern.
- cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing) is also likely as the paper discusses the use of virtual machines in cloud environments.
- cs.SE (Software Engineering) is another possible category as the paper proposes a framework for detecting covert channels in cloud environments using machine learning.
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a possible category as the paper uses Support Vector Machines for building and training the model.
- cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) is also a possible category as the paper discusses the use of traditional security measures employed in firewalls etc in a network.
